Transit & Map Visualization API Documentation
1. Overview
Base Router Path: /transit
This section covers the transit data endpoints, providing access to routes, real-time vehicle locations, and stop information for both PRT and CMU systems.
Base Router Path: /map
This section covers the map configuration endpoints.

